      "detail": "Human oversight requirements in the AI Act mandate meaningful human review of AI decisions. This creates a human-review alignment method layered on top of technical approaches like RLHF. The regulatory framework treats human review as a necessary complement to technical alignment. This approach scales better for accountability than for capability growth."
    },
