      "detail": "GDPR's security requirements and AI Act risk-management obligations mandate robust security measures. Enterprise-grade controls are the minimum compliance standard for high-risk AI deployments. This exceeds the US API-keys default but falls short of defense-grade for most commercial use. Security posture is a regulatory requirement rather than a market choice."
    },
